<Defs>

	<ThingDef ParentName="CGF1_MWP_BaseMakeableMeleeWeapon">
		<defName>CGF1_MWP_Shinigami</defName>
		<label>Shinigami</label>
		<description>A father must wear a crown. He is cunning, he is the moon. One who seeks only to consume. Half where all is dark, and nothing speaks. In the presence of the father, lay only empty space. No choice but to march into his deceptive embrace. For a mother, give her a sword. Blazes as the sun, fierce, strong. She bears all, she gives but does not take. Half where all is bright, and all stands true. In the mother's light, there can be no void. As she wields her divine, burning weapon, the world remains. But their child needs only dirt. Between heaven and hell, they embody the Earth. The gift to men, of men, for men. Wearing its crown and wielding its sword. The child, the scion, two gifts. The dividing line, promised sun and forgotten moon.</description>
